Git is distrubuted vesrion control System. Linux Torvald introduced the git after they tie break up with  the bitkkeeper in the year 1995.
Git is free and open source tool.
In git every client as copy of the file and has a complete history on it. Client pushes the code from working to STG then from to main branch. After from main branch code is oushed to central repository.
We can use in git in offile source also beacuse it is having local repository.
Git is having 3 stages. Working directory, Staging area, local repository.
